'''王薇薇'''<ref>{{cite news |author1=Vanessa Friedman |coauthor=王相宜(译) |date=2014-09-15 |title=设计师王薇薇的房间，那里什么都没有 |script-title=Vera Wang: Treasuring the Calm in the Eye of the Storm |url=https://cn.nytimes.com/fashion/20140915/t15verawang/zh-hans/ |newspaper=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |location=[[纽约市|纽约市]] |publisher={{Link-en|纽约时报公司|The New York Times Company}} |access-date=2020-05-16 }}</ref>（{{Lang-en|Vera Wang}}；{{bd|1949年|6月27日|||catIdx=Wang}}），著名[[美国华裔|美国华裔]][[時尚設計|时尚设计师]]，主要活跃在[[纽约市|纽约市]]。

== 早年履历 ==
王薇薇出生于[[美国|美国]][[纽约市|纽约市]]的一个[[美籍华裔|华裔]]家庭，并在纽约市长大；她出生时所使用的英文名为{{lang|en|Vera Ellen Wang}}。王薇薇的父母都出生于[[中国|中国]]，并于1940年代中期移民至美国。王薇薇的父亲王澄清毕业于[[燕京大学|燕京大学]]和[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]，拥有一家医药公司；母亲吴赤芳曾经在[[联合国|联合国]]担任[[翻译|翻译]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=鄢云 |title=时尚界的婚纱女王（华人故事） |url=http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrbhwb/html/2010-07/30/content_582773.htm |website=[[人民网|人民网]] |publisher=[[人民日报|人民日报（海外版）]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100802132643/http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrbhwb/html/2010-07/30/content_582773.htm |archive-date=2010-08-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而王薇薇的外祖父是[[奉系|奉系军阀]]的[[吴俊陞|吴俊陞]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=程佳 |author2=楹楹 |title=独家揭秘国际名媛舞会：一张入场券要十万 |url=https://ent.qq.com/a/20150101/021379.htm |website=[[腾讯网|腾讯网]] |publisher=腾讯娱乐 |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2015-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815062928/http://ent.qq.com/a/20150101/021379.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，于1928年的[[皇姑屯事件|皇姑屯事件]]中被[[日本关东军|日本关东军]]暗杀<ref>{{cite web |author1=毕玮琳 |author2=李萱 |title=从清朝的“勇将”到民国的“福将” |url=http://jlrbszb.cnjiwang.com/pc/paper/c/201905/10/content_80414.html |website=中国吉林网 |publisher=吉林日报 |accessdate=2020-05-16}}</ref>。王薇薇还有一个弟弟，名叫肯尼斯·王（Kenneth Wang）<ref>{{cite web |title=王薇薇父紅顏知己爭產敗訴 |url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20120420/00180_006.html |publisher=[[东方日报|东方日报]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427000704/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20120420/00180_006.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

王薇薇曾就读于{{Link-en|友谊学校|Friends Seminary}}<ref>{{cite web |author1=Emma Allen |title=Going Once, Going Twice |url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2015/04/13/art-and-commerce-going-once-going-twice |publisher=[[纽约客|纽约客]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116020841/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2015/04/13/art-and-commerce-going-once-going-twice |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并在1967年从{{Link-en|查宾学校|Chapin School}}毕业<ref>{{cite web |author1=Andrew Seguin |title=Vera Wang: From the ice to the runway |url=http://www.chapin.edu/cf_news/view.cfm?newsid=333 |publisher={{Link-en|查宾学校|Chapin School}} |accessdate=2020-05-16}}</ref>。高中毕业后，她就读于巴黎大学<ref>{{cite web |author1=Favour |title=Vera Wang Looks Nothing Like Her Age & Her Abs Are Proof Of That |url=https://theblast.com/130087/vera-wang-looks-nothing-like-her-age-her-abs-are-proof-of-that |publisher=The Blast |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520110713/https://theblast.com/130087/vera-wang-looks-nothing-like-her-age-her-abs-are-proof-of-that |dead-url=no }}</ref>并在[[莎拉·劳伦斯学院|莎拉·劳伦斯学院]]获得[[美术史|美术史]]学位<ref>{{cite web |author1=Surya Naga Devi Bonthu |title=Vera Wang Net Worth 2020 All You Need to Know |url=https://xdigitalnews.com/vera-wang-net-worth-2020-all-you-need-to-know/21667/ |publisher=X Digital News |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203134817/https://xdigitalnews.com/vera-wang-net-worth-2020-all-you-need-to-know/21667/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

王薇薇从8岁的时候就开始学习[[花样滑冰|花样滑冰]]<ref name="nyt111220">{{cite news |url=https://tmagazine.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/12/20/vera-on-ice/ |title=Vera on Ice |first=Edward |last=Barsamian |work=The New York Times |date=December 20, 2011 |accessdate=December 20, 2011 |archive-date=2019-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213154137/https://tmagazine.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/12/20/vera-on-ice/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在高中时代，她与詹姆斯·斯图亚特（{{lang|en|James Stuart}}）成为[[双人滑|双人滑]]搭档并一起接受训练。他俩曾参加过1968年的[[美国花样滑冰锦标赛|美国花样滑冰锦标赛]]；并在1968年1月9日，王薇薇登上了《[[体育画报|体育画报]]》的“{{Link-en|芸芸众生 (体育画报)|Faces in the Crowd (Sports Illustrated)|芸芸众生}}”版。由于未能入选[[奧林匹克運動會美國代表團|美国国奥队]]，她转投时尚行业<ref>{{cite book |author1=Katherine E. Krohn |title=Vera Wang |date=2006 |publisher=Twenty-First Century Books |isbn=9780822566120 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xmJ7doZXP0QC |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2014-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628092703/http://books.google.com/books?id=xmJ7doZXP0QC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过时至今日，王薇薇依旧享受滑冰的乐趣，并表示“滑冰是多方面的”<ref name="nyt111220" />。

1968年，在[[纽约华尔道夫酒店|纽约华尔道夫酒店]]举办的{{Link-en|国际元媛舞会|International Debutante Ball}}上，王薇薇{{Link-en|名媛初登场|Debutante|首次亮相}}于[[上流社会|上流社会]]<ref>{{cite book |author1=Katherine E. Krohn |title=Vera Wang: Enduring Style |date=2008 |publisher=Twenty-First Century Books |isbn=9781580135726 |page=92 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hd0PrIc9S3AC&pg=PA92&lpg=PA92&dq=vera+wang+international+debutante+ball&source=bl&ots=SNcW0F1zK0&sig=mVGSR6HJd8AAUsC6mSyYDi5YKPo&hl=nl&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjUuv3YwrDYAhUHxiYKHXGoC38Q6AEIYDAL#v=onepage&q=vera%20wang%20international%20debutante%20ball&f=false |accessdate=2020-05-16}}</ref>。

== 职业生涯 ==
[[File:Vera_Wang_Spring-Summer_2014_04.jpg|thumb]]上的王薇薇春夏装走秀。]]

王薇薇刚从[[莎拉·劳伦斯学院|莎拉·劳伦斯学院]]毕业就被聘为《[[时尚_(杂志)|时尚]]》杂志的编辑，这使得她成为《时尚》史上最年轻的编辑。她在《时尚》工作了17年，于1987年辞职并加入到[[拉尔夫·劳伦|拉尔夫·劳伦]]并在那工作了2年。当王薇薇40岁的时候，她辞职成为独立的新娘婚纱设计师。她设计名单中的公众人物包括：[[切尔西·克林顿|切尔西·克林顿]]<ref name="Vogue">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.vogue.com/946729/brides-who-wore-vera-wang-wedding-dresses |title=The 12 Most Stunning Vera Wang Brides |magazine=[[时尚_(杂志)|时尚]] |date=2014-06-27 |access-date=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2016-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224213033/http://www.vogue.com/946729/brides-who-wore-vera-wang-wedding-dresses// |dead-url=no }}</ref>、{{Link-en|卡蕾娜·戈尔|Karenna Gore}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://edition.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1997/07/12/gore.wedding |title=Gore's Eldest Daughter Weds New York Doctor In Washington |work=[[CNN|CNN]] |date=1997-07-12 |accessdate=2009-06-04 |archive-date=2009-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090121153758/http://edition.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1997/07/12/gore.wedding/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[伊万卡·特朗普|伊万卡·特朗普]]<ref name="Vogue" />、{{Link-en|坎贝尔·布朗|Campbell Brown (journalist)}}<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1179281,00.html |title=NBC's Campbell Brown Gets Married |magazine=[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]] |date=2006-04-02 |access-date=2009-06-04 |archive-date=2009-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090602100844/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1179281,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[艾莉西亚·凯斯|艾莉西亚·凯斯]]<ref name="Vogue" />、[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]<ref name="Vogue" />、[[维多利亚·贝克汉姆|维多利亚·贝克汉姆]]<ref name="Vogue" />、[[莎拉·米歇尔·盖拉|莎拉·米歇尔·盖拉]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://celebritybrideguide.com/sarah-michelle-gellar-freddie-prinze-jr-wedding/ |title=Sarah Michelle Gellar and Freddie Prinze Jr. Wedding |work=Celebrity Bride Guide |date=2002-09-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208132601/http://celebritybrideguide.com/sarah-michelle-gellar-freddie-prinze-jr-wedding/ |archivedate=2009-02-08 |accessdate=2020-05-16 }}</ref>、[[艾薇儿·拉维尼|艾薇儿·拉维尼]]<ref name="Vogue" />、[[希拉里·达夫|希拉里·达夫]]<ref name="Vogue" />、[[科勒·卡戴珊|科勒·卡戴珊]]<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.hellomagazine.com/brides/gallery/2013101315041/Vera-wang-brides-celebrity-dresses/3/ |title=Celebrities who wore Vera Wang on their wedding day |magazine=[[Hello!|Hello!]] |date=2013-10-13 |page=3 |access-date=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306235513/https://www.hellomagazine.com/brides/gallery/2013101315041/Vera-wang-brides-celebrity-dresses/3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[金·卡戴珊|金·卡戴珊]]<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.hellomagazine.com/brides/gallery/2013101315041/Vera-wang-brides-celebrity-dresses/4/ |title=Celebrities who wore Vera Wang on their wedding day |magazine=Hello! |date=2013-10-13 |page=4 |access-date=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2018-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180811113903/https://www.hellomagazine.com/brides/gallery/2013101315041/Vera-wang-brides-celebrity-dresses/4/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>等人。[[米歇尔·奥巴马|米歇尔·奥巴马]]也穿过王薇薇所设计的晚礼服<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://fashion.elle.com/fashion/insider/2011/12/05/michelle-obama-dons-vera-wang/ |title=Michelle Obama Dons Vera Wang |magazine=[[ELLE|ELLE]] |date=2011-12-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120711150117/http://fashion.elle.com/fashion/insider/2011/12/05/michelle-obama-dons-vera-wang/ |archivedate=2012-07-11 |accessdate=2020-05-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.vogue.com/fashion/10-best-dressed/tis-the-season/ |title=Photos: 10 Best Dressed: Week of December 12, 2011 |magazine=时尚 |date=2011-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120215171749/http://www.vogue.com/fashion/10-best-dressed/tis-the-season/ |archivedate=2012-02-15 |accessdate=2020-05-16 }}</ref>。

她也曾经为[[花样滑冰|花样滑冰]]运动员设计表演服，这其中包括[[南茜·克里根|南茜·克里根]]、[[关颖珊|关颖珊]]、[[埃文·莱萨塞克|埃文·莱萨塞克]]和[[陈巍|陈巍]]等。王薇薇分别设计了[[南茜·克里根|南茜·克里根]]在[[1992年冬季奥林匹克运动会|1992年]]和[[1994年冬季奥林匹克运动会|1994年冬奥会]]的服装；[[关颖珊|关颖珊]]在[[1998年冬季奥林匹克运动会|1998年]]和[[2002年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2002年冬奥会]]的服装；[[埃文·莱萨塞克|埃文·莱萨塞克]]在[[2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2010年冬奥会]]的服装以及[[陈巍|陈巍]]在[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2018年]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=Kaitlyn Frey |title=Vera Wang Reflects on More Than 20 Years of Designing Olympic Figure Skating Costumes |url=https://people.com/style/vera-wang-interview-design-figure-skating-costumes/ |publisher=[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200501105224/https://people.com/style/vera-wang-interview-design-figure-skating-costumes/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[2022年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2022年冬奥会]]的服装<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://people.com/style/beijing-olympics-2022-vera-wang-praises-nathan-chens-record-breaking-win/ | title = NVera Wang Praises Nathan Chen's Record-Breaking Win, Calls Dressing Olympian a 'Privilege'  | date = 10/2/22 | publisher = [[人物_(雜誌)|人物]] }}</ref>。王薇薇因为在服装设计方面对花样滑冰运动的贡献而在2009年入选{{Link-en|美国花样滑冰名人堂|United States Figure Skating Hall of Fame}}<ref>{{cite web |author1=Kelly Whiteside |title=Johnny Weir, Evan Lysacek in battle at figure skating nationals |url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/olympics/2009-01-21-figure-skating-championships_N.htm |publisher=[[今日美国报|今日美国报]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310182041/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/olympics/2009-01-21-figure-skating-championships_N.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同时，王薇薇还为[[费城老鹰|费城老鹰]]{{Link-en|费城老鹰啦啦队|Philadelphia Eagles Cheerleaders|啦啦队}}设计了制服<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.philadelphiaeagles.com/cheerleaders/highlights.html |title=Highlights |work=[[费城老鹰|费城老鹰]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429164743/https://www.philadelphiaeagles.com/cheerleaders/highlights.html |archivedate=2011-04-29 |accessdate=2020-05-16 }}</ref>。

在许多红毯走秀环节上，明星们也热衷于穿着王薇薇所设计的礼服。维奥拉·戴维斯在2012年[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]红毯以及[[索菲娅·维加拉|索菲娅·维加拉]]在第65届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]红毯上都是穿着她的设计<ref>{{cite web |author1=[[BBC|BBC]] |title=Oscars 2012: Stars arrive |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-17174658 |website=[[BBC在线|BBC在线]] |publisher=[[BBC新闻|BBC新闻]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903070630/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-17174658 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Rose Curiel |title=Sofía Vergara Talks Wedding Dress: It Has to Be Vera Wang |url=https://www.eonline.com/news/465262/sofia-vergara-reveals-she-ll-marry-in-a-cleavage-baring-vera-wang-get-all-the-details-on-her-fab-gown |website={{Link-en|娱乐新闻 (美国)|E! News|娱乐新闻}} |publisher={{Link-en|娱乐频道 (美国)|E!|娱乐频道}} |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302092317/https://www.eonline.com/news/465262/sofia-vergara-reveals-she-ll-marry-in-a-cleavage-baring-vera-wang-get-all-the-details-on-her-fab-gown |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2001年10月23日，王薇薇的个人著作《王薇薇：完美婚礼》出版。2005年6月，她荣膺{{Link-en|美国时装设计师协会|Council of Fashion Designers of America}}“年度女装设计师”称号；2006年5月27日，她获得了[[萨凡纳艺术设计学院|萨凡纳艺术设计学院]]“{{Link-en|安德烈·莱昂·塔利|André Leon Talley}}终身成就奖”；2013年，王薇薇被美国时装设计师协会授予“终身成就奖”<ref>{{cite web |title=Vera Wang honored for lifetime achievement |url=https://www.dispatch.com/content/stories/life_and_entertainment/2013/06/05/vera-wang-honored-for-lifetime-achievement.html |publisher={{Link-en|哥伦布新闻报道|The Columbus Dispatch}} |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302090547/https://www.dispatch.com/content/stories/life_and_entertainment/2013/06/05/vera-wang-honored-for-lifetime-achievement.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Vera Wang |url=https://cfda.com/members/profile/vera-wang |publisher={{Link-en|美国时装设计师协会|Council of Fashion Designers of America}} |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302090511/https://cfda.com/members/profile/vera-wang |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006年，王薇薇与连锁百货商{{Link-en|科尔氏|Kohl's}}达成一项合作协议，为它们提供一条平价成衣产品线，该品牌被命名为“简薇（{{lang|en|Simply Vera}}）”<ref>{{cite web |title=Commercial Success and Expansion - Vera Wang |url=https://www.biography.com/fashion-designer/vera-wang#commercial-success |publisher={{Link-en|FYI频道|FYI (American TV channel)|人物传记频道}} |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520111202/https://www.biography.com/fashion-designer/vera-wang#commercial-success |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年，《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志将其列为“2018年美国白手起家女性富豪榜”的第34位，当时她的收入已经增至6.3亿[[美元|美元]]。

在持续2年仅仅通过视频介绍自己设计系列的休假期后，王薇薇于2019年9月10日回归[[纽约时装周|纽约时装周]]，公开在其品牌的2020年春夏款走秀中亮相，以庆祝她的品牌成立30周年<ref>{{cite web |author1=Jocelyn Noveck |title=Vera Wang returns, with hippie hair and couture lingerie |url=https://news.yahoo.com/vera-wang-returns-hippie-hair-214308733.html |website=[[雅虎新闻|雅虎新闻]] |publisher=[[美联社|美联社]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010163519/https://news.yahoo.com/vera-wang-returns-hippie-hair-214308733.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Annabella Winsteald |title=Vera Wang Spring Summer 2020 Full Fashion Show (untagged) |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mkax-LFPxmQ |website=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124071536/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mkax-LFPxmQ&gl=US&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这次走秀获得了大量积极评价，戈德弗雷·蒂尼（{{lang|en|Godfrey Deeny}}）将其描述为“少数几个拥有真正独特时尚基因的纽约设计师之一所缔造的著名系列”<ref>{{cite web |author1=Godfrey Deeny |title=Vera Wang soars yet stumbles |url=https://in.fashionnetwork.com/news/Vera-wang-soars-yet-stumbles,1135695.html |publisher=FashionNetwork.com |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010163524/https://in.fashionnetwork.com/news/Vera-wang-soars-yet-stumbles,1135695.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而布里奇特·福利（{{lang|en|Bridget Foley}}）则将王薇薇的设计形容为“以勇敢的姿态所呈现的美丽而精心设计的服装”<ref>{{cite web |author1=Bridget Foley |title=Vera Wang RTW Spring 2020 |url=https://wwd.com/runway/spring-ready-to-wear-2020/new-york/vera-wang/review/ |publisher=[[女装日报|女装日报]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010163523/https://wwd.com/runway/spring-ready-to-wear-2020/new-york/vera-wang/review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是这场秀的完美却受到了几次鞋品故障的破坏<ref name="Friedman">{{cite web |author1=Vanessa Friedman |title=What to Wear to Womansplain |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/11/style/proenza-schouler-gabriela-hearst-new-york-fashion-week.html |publisher=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505130233/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/11/style/proenza-schouler-gabriela-hearst-new-york-fashion-week.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Nicole Phelps |title=Vera Wang Spring 2020 Ready-to-Wear Collection |url=https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/spring-2020-ready-to-wear/vera-wang |publisher=[[时尚_(杂志)|时尚]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010163521/https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/spring-2020-ready-to-wear/vera-wang |dead-url=no }}</ref>，特别是在结尾部分，有不少于四名[[模特儿|模特儿]]因此而摔倒<ref>{{cite web |author1=Annabella Winsteald |title=Models trip and fall at Vera Wang Spring/Summer 2020 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sq4j6kR0IWY |website=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124071536/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sq4j6kR0IWY&gl=US&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这其中也包括顶级超模[[孫菲菲_(模特兒)|孙菲菲]]，她在走秀中曾两次摔倒<ref>{{cite web |author1=Annabella Winsteald |title=op Model Fei Fei Sun FALLS TWICE during Vera Wang Spring/Summer 2020 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6AJf1s9rKE |website=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124071531/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6AJf1s9rKE&gl=US&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。知名时尚评论员{{Link-en|凡妮莎·费尔德曼|Vanessa Friedman}}对此评论道，“都已经是2019年了，任何女人都不该因为自己的穿着而遭受酷刑。”<ref name="Friedman" />

=== 主要产业 ===
1990年，王薇薇在[[纽约市|纽约市]]的{{Link-en|卡莱尔酒店|Carlyle Hotel}}创立了自己的设计沙龙，并在此出售她的品牌婚纱<ref name="nymag">{{cite news |url=http://nymag.com/fashion/fashionshows/designers/bios/verawang/ |title=Vera Wang - New York Fashion Designer |work=[[紐約_(雜誌)|纽约]] |date=2005 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060831130236/http://nymag.com/fashion/fashionshows/designers/bios/verawang/ |archivedate=2006-08-31 |accessdate=2020-05-16 }}</ref>。此后，王薇薇在[[纽约|纽约]]、[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[东京|东京]]和[[悉尼|悉尼]]都开设了她的婚纱专卖店，同时她的经营范围也扩展到[[香水|香水]]、珠宝、眼镜和家庭用品等。

2002年，王薇薇开始涉足家庭时尚行业，并推出了“王薇薇瓷器与水晶系列（{{lang|en|The Vera Wang China and Crystal Collection}}）”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.fashionxstyles.com/2014/11/vera-wang-bridal-pink-outfit-collection-by-audrey-hepburn/ |title=Vera Wang – Bridal Pink Outfit Collection by Audrey Hepburn |work=Fashion X Styles |date=2014-11-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224170249/http://www.fashionxstyles.com/2014/11/vera-wang-bridal-pink-outfit-collection-by-audrey-hepburn/ |archivedate=2015-02-24 |accessdate=2020-05-16 }}</ref>。2007年，王薇薇与{{Link-en|科尔氏|Kohl's}}合作了她的首个品牌{{Link-en|副线|Diffusion line}}——“简薇（{{lang|en|Simply Vera}}）”，该系列仅在科尔氏出售<ref name="nymag" />。“纯白王薇薇（{{lang|en|White by Vera Wang}}）”于2011年2月11日在{{Link-en|大卫新娘|David's Bridal}}创立，这是王薇薇品牌的副线品牌。这个品牌的婚纱售价从600美元到1400美元不等，这使得更多新娘可以以更平价的方式穿着王薇薇所设计的婚纱<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.davidsbridal.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/PressRoom_Davids-Bridal-White-by-Vera-Wang-Launches |title=White by Vera Wang launches at David's Bridal |work={{Link-en|大卫新娘|David's Bridal}} |date=2011-02-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110307040053/https://www.davidsbridal.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/PressRoom_Davids-Bridal-White-by-Vera-Wang-Launches |archivedate=2011-03-07 |accessdate=2020-05-16 }}</ref>。

2012年春季，王薇薇与{{Link-en|裁缝品牌|Tailored Brands|男士衣坊}}达成合作，以零售或租借铺位的形式出售[[无尾礼服|无尾礼服]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Men's Wearhouse Partners With Vera Wang to Launch Black by Vera Wang |url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/mens-wearhouse-partners-with-vera-wang-to-launch-black-by-vera-wang-135645733.html |publisher=[[美通社|美通社]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2019-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302090800/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/mens-wearhouse-partners-with-vera-wang-to-launch-black-by-vera-wang-135645733.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年6月，王薇薇在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]开设了“王薇薇新娘雪梨店”；并在[[韩国|韩国]]开设了她的首家亚洲旗舰店“王薇薇新娘首尔店”<ref>{{cite web |author1=Rachel Lee |title=Vera Wang opens 1st Asia flagship in Seoul |url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2012/10/199_114120.html |publisher=[[韩国时报|韩国时报]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004213532/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2012/10/199_114120.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 个人生活 ==
1989年，王薇薇嫁给了{{Link-en|亚瑟·贝克尔|Arthur P. Becker}}，这是一场[[浸礼宗|浸礼宗]]与{{Link-en|犹太教中的异教婚姻|Interfaith marriage in Judaism|犹太教}}的{{Link-en|异教婚姻|Interfaith marriage}}<ref name="#1"/><ref name="todd">{{cite book |author1=Anne M. Todd |title=Vera Wang |date=2007 |publisher=Infobase Publishing |isbn=9781438100388 |page=45,107 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GMeeM3sc4pgC&pg=PA45&lpg=PA45&dq=vera+wang+adopted&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=adopted&f=false |accessdate=2020-05-16}}</ref>。他们与他们所领养的两个女儿居住于[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]<ref name="todd" />，大女儿塞西莉亚（{{lang|en|Cecilia}}）出生于1990年，目前已分家另过于纽约市；小女儿约瑟芬（{{lang|en|Josephine}}）出生于1993年，自{{Link-en|查宾学校|Chapin School}}毕业后，目前就读于[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]。贝克尔曾是一家信息技术服务公司{{Link-en|时代华纳有线|Time Warner Cable|导航站}}的首席执行官，但于2010年8月离职。2012年7月，王薇薇公司发表声明，宣布两人已经友好分手<ref>{{cite web |title=Vera Wang, Arthur Becker Separate After 23 Years Of Marriage |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/11/vera-wang-arthur-becker-separate-_n_1664277.html |publisher=[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2017-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731011728/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/11/vera-wang-arthur-becker-separate-_n_1664277.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

王薇薇热爱运动和锻炼。她每天忙于处理自己名下不同系列的产品，从细心研究瓷器图案到{{Link-en|科尔氏|Kohl's}}的小型皮革产品。她通常在白天的时候不接听电话<ref>{{cite web |author1=Elisa Lipsky-karasz |title=My List: Vera Wang in 24 Hours |url=https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/designers/a910/24-hours-with-vera-wang-1112/ |publisher=[[时尚芭莎|时尚芭莎]] |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2020-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515221300/https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/designers/a910/24-hours-with-vera-wang-1112/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 跨界经历 ==
美国的数部影视作品及电视节目里都有提及王薇薇或有她出镜。

在电视剧版的《[[欲望都市|欲望都市]]》里，女主角之一的[[夏绿蒂·约克|夏绿蒂·约克]]发现王薇薇所设计的婚纱是最完美的婚纱，因而在她与特瑞·麦克道格尔（{{lang|en|Trey MacDougal}}）的婚礼上选择穿着她的设计<ref>{{cite book |author1=Amy Sohn |coauthors=Sarah Jessica Parker(撰) |author2=Sarah Wildman |title=Sex and the City: Kiss and Tell |date=2004 |publisher=Simon and Schuster |isbn=9780743457309 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rrOIWxT8mmIC |accessdate=2020-05-17 |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627191821/http://books.google.com/books?id=rrOIWxT8mmIC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[国家广播公司|NBC电视网]]首播的电视剧《[[白宫群英|白宫群英]]》中，她的设计也在第三季第19集的“{{Link-en|白宫群英 (第三季)|The West Wing (season 3)|黑色婚纱}}”中被提及。而在[[美国广播公司|ABC电视网]]播出的电视剧《[[丑女贝蒂|丑女贝蒂]]》中，王薇薇更是[[友情客串|亲自出镜]]，她在剧中为威廉米娜·斯莱特（{{lang|en|Wilhelmina Slater}}）设计了她与布拉德福德·米德（{{lang|en|Bradford Meade}}）婚礼上的礼服。

